    public static class CarbonExtension.Private
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.ExtensionElement
    Stanza(/Packet) extension indicating that a message may not be carbon-copied. Adding this extension to any message will disallow that message from being copied.
